“Center experiment samplng 2.xlsx” data

Loading & cleaning the data

DataRaw <- read.xlsx(
  file = "Center experiment samplng 2.xlsx",
  sheetIndex = 1, startRow = 3, stringsAsFactors = F)

DataRaw <- DataRaw %>% as_tibble %>%
  setNames(c("Samples", "SoilType", "Treatment",
             "Donor", "Nem", "Egg",
             "EggsNem", "WtShtFrsh",
             "WtShtDry", "WtRootFresh", "ToRemove")) %>% 
  dplyr::select(-ToRemove, -WtShtDry) %>% 
  # dplyr::filter(SoilType != "Lucklum") %>%
  
  mutate(
    Treatment = replace(Treatment, Treatment == "E.mustard", "Mustard"),
    Treatment = replace(Treatment, Treatment == "free microbiome", "Free"),
    SoilType = replace(SoilType, SoilType == "Ahlum_Ã–ko", "AhlumOko"),
    SoilType = replace(SoilType, SoilType == "Ahlum_conventional ", "AhlumCon")) %>%
  
  mutate(SoilType = factor(SoilType, levels = unique(SoilType)),
         Treatment = factor(Treatment, levels = unique(Treatment)),
         Donor = factor(Donor, levels = unique(Donor)),
         Nem = round(Nem), Egg = round(Egg),
         EggsNem = round(EggsNem),
         WtRootFresh = as.numeric(WtRootFresh),
         WtShtFrsh = as.numeric(WtShtFrsh))
